<div data-slate-editor="true" data-key="2398" autocorrect="off" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" style="outline: none; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><div class="se-29a3d684" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2399"><img class="se-a236460a" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/ca/a6/cayy6e0bab6307b7647fdd96e77dbba6.png?wh=1254x708"></div><div class="se-d7ac8d47  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2400"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2401"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2401:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你好，我是黄佳。欢迎进入第一个模式组——</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2402"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2402:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-64e73952" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">感知模式</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2403"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2403:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c6bec807  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2404"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2405"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2405:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">正题开始之前，请你先思考个重要问题：归根结底，感知和记忆都是 Context Engineering 的一部分，那么为什么要拆成感知和记忆两个模式组？如果你已经在生产实践中建设自己的 Agent，那么你哪些时候是在设计感知？哪些时候是在设计记忆？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-57f57993" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2406"><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2407"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2408"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2408:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">没有标准答案，只是想启发你的思考。因为有时候我也觉得二者的边界有些模糊。但是把它理得更清晰，显然有助于我们思考得更深。希望讲完感知模式组和记忆模式组之后，我们建立更深入的认知。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-8b5b8348  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2409"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2410"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2410:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这一模块讨论一个看似简单、但在生产系统里极其关键的问题：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2411"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2411:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c8e54cc0" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">怎样让 Agent 看对东西</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2412"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2412:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-19fee8b6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2413"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2414"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2414:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">传统软件没有这道工序。函数的输入是被 schema 严格定义的，调用方传什么就处理什么，工程师不用操心“该让谁进”。Agent 不一样，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2415"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2415:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6b1857fd" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">它的输入是 prompt 这种自由文本，谁进 prompt、谁不进、按什么顺序进、压缩到什么粒度，全是工程师的设计决策</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2416"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2416:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。每一个进入 prompt 的 token 都在花预算：attention 预算、KV cache 空间、API 计费。Perception 就是在管这笔预算。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e6894730" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2417"><img class="se-5d62440c" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/a8/y6/a83fd39b76d3b9c9bd095d00d5287yy6.jpg?wh=1448x1086"></div><div class="se-956babf3  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2418"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2419"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2419:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">很多时候，模型已经足够强，prompt 也写得很认真，Agent 给出的答案看起来通顺、引用具体、逻辑自洽，但最后一核对，事实是错的。把 trace 拉出来看，问题往往不在推理阶段，而在最前面：它一开始就没有看到关键材料。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-134c07d8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2420"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2421"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2421:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">在 Agent 系统里，感知不是一个外围模块，它其实决定了后面所有推理的上限。模型并不是在真实世界里推理，它是在你喂给它的那一小块上下文里推理。它看不到的事实，对它来说就不存在；它看到的噪声太多，也会稀释真正重要的证据。一个中等模型读干净的 30K token，很多时候比最强模型淹在 180K 噪声里更可靠。差距不一定来自模型能力，而是来自它到底看到了什么。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-cf65566a" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2422"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2423"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2423:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知是 PRA 循环里的入口闸</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-9b170d43  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2424"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2425"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2425:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">除了双轴框架那张图，这门课贯穿始终的另一张图是 PRA 循环：Perception、Reasoning、Action，也就是感知、推理、行动。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c64c50fb  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2426"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2427"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2427:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">行动负责把决策变成对外部世界的影响。感知站在另一头，负责把外部世界压缩成模型能处理的上下文。而推理只能加工已经进入上下文的材料，它不能凭空补回没看见的事实。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-60fd2b35" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2428"><img class="se-34fbbbfb" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/8a/e9/8a8bbc33c9e0f39d375df726a2a5eae9.jpg?wh=9280x5572"></div><div class="se-1092c2e9  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2429"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2430"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2430:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">很多失败案例的根因都是：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b2a3fcc5" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2431"><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2432"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2433"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2433:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">“Agent 不知道 X”的真相，往往是“X 明明存在，但没有进入它的视野”。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-6bce1b66  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2434"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2435"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2435:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这也是为什么长上下文不能简单理解成“仓库越塞越全”。Liu 等人在 TACL 2024 的论文《</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2436" class="se-f828cddd se-8ab6c248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2437"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2437:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Lost in the Middle</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2438"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2438:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">》里发现，模型使用长上下文时，对开头和结尾的信息更敏感，中间位置的关键信息更容易被忽略。窗口变长以后，问题不会自动消失，很多时候只是把“没检索到”变成了“检索到了但没用上”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ff6954c8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2439"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2440"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2440:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Anthropic 在 </span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2441" class="se-f828cddd se-8ab6c248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2442"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2442:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">《Effective Context Engineering for AI Agents》</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2443"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2443:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">里告诉我们，上下文工程是“在恰当的时刻把恰当的信息放进上下文窗口的精细工艺”。同时也把感知工程师的工作定义为找出“</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2444"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2444:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-28144a73" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">使下一次推理质量最大化的最小高信号 token 集合</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2445"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2445:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">”。佳哥觉得这个定义对于我们的工作非常有指导意义，所以特别强调一下。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4b7e4aa1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2446"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2447"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2447:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这里可以用一个很简单的例子理解。假设用户问：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-578b76e5" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2448"><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2449"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2450"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2450:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这个订单能不能退款？</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-1186dd96  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2451"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2452"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2452:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一个粗糙的感知系统，可能会这样做：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e28b315a" data-code-language="javascript" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2453"><div class="se-42ab5d43 se-6698d8ef"><span></span></div><div class="se-d060ec15 se-490c5851"><span></span></div><div class="se-a990b271"><div class="se-3cf6e5c0 se-657c67d8" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-3cf6e5c0 se-657c67d8" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-3cf6e5c0 se-657c67d8" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-3cf6e5c0 se-657c67d8" data-code-line-number="4"></div></div><div class="se-9ab14a49"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2454"></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2455"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2456"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2456:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">context = </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2457"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2457:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-title function_" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">search_docs</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2458"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2458:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">(query=</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2459"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2459:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-string" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">"退款"</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2460"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2460:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">, top_k=</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2461"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2461:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-number" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">50</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2462"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2462:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2463"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2464"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2464:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">answer = </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2465"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2465:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-title function_" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">llm</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2466"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2466:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">(question, context)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2467"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 80px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-3ad2c9be  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2468"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2469"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2469:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">看起来很合理。多找一点资料，给模型更多上下文。但问题是，</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2470" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2471"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2471:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">top_k=50</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2472"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2472:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 里可能混着旧版退款政策、无关 FAQ、历史客服话术、其他品类规则。模型不是没能力，而是被放进了一个很脏的信息现场。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a8cfbd6d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2473"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2474"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2474:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">更好的感知，不是“多塞”，而是先判断这次推理真正需要什么：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3244c80f" data-code-language="python" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2475"><div class="se-d3c9e062 se-e61768f0"><span></span></div><div class="se-73f88d5c se-42a6e1a1"><span></span></div><div class="se-39a14886"><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="8"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="9"></div><div class="se-42bd215e se-9fc76d9f" data-code-line-number="10"></div></div><div class="se-9502e4ca"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2476"></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2477"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2478"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2478:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">context = [</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2479"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2480"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2480:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">    order.status,              </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2481"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2481:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-comment" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true"># 订单当前状态</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2482"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2483"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2483:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">    order.delivered_at,        </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2484"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2484:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-comment" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true"># 是否已签收、签收多久</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2485"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2486"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2486:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">    user.refund_history,       </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2487"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2487:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-comment" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true"># 是否有异常退款记录</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2488"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2489"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2489:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">    current_refund_policy,     </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2490"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2490:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-comment" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true"># 当前生效的退款规则</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2491"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2492"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2492:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">    sku.refund_exceptions      </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2493"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2493:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-comment" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true"># 这个商品有没有特殊限制</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2494"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2495"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2495:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">]</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2496"></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2497"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2498"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2498:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">answer = llm(question, context)</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 200px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-30907b1c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2499"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2500"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2500:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这就是最小高信号 token 集合的意思，不是把所有和“退款”沾边的材料都塞进去，而是把这次判断真正需要的证据放进去。感知工程解决的不是一个简单的“检索多少条”的问题，而是三个更架构化的问题：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c855e8c2" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2501"><div class="se-1112f856 se-d0992704" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2502"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2503"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2503:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-cbee6624" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">什么信息有资格进入上下文？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-a1678769 se-688de32a" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2504"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2505"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2505:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-842e6dee" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">什么信息应该被压缩、排序或丢弃？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-f28d5b46 se-5756cf55" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2506"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2507"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2507:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ef0c42e9" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">什么信息必须在模型推理前就被结构化出来？</span></span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-6000a749  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2508"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2509"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2509:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这样再回到 PRA 循环里就很清楚了：Reasoning 的质量，不只取决于模型怎么想，也取决于 Perception 先把一个什么样的世界交给了它。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2ed1e0ec  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2510"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2511"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2511:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以，感知不是普通的预处理步骤。它更像 Agent 系统里的入口闸：哪些事实能进来，按什么顺序进来，以什么颗粒度进来，决定了后面的 Reasoning 有没有可靠材料可用。到了生产系统里，这件事和数据建模、API 设计、容量规划一样，都是架构问题。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-a7ddc802" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2512"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2513"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2513:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知模式组中的四种模式</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-e82a0658  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2514"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2515"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2515:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知模式组包含如下图所示的四种模式，我们的讲解顺序是上下文分诊 &nbsp;Context Triage、语义压缩 Semantic Compaction、渐进发现 &nbsp;Progressive Discovery 以及多模态融合 Multi-Modal Fusion。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b5c16551" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2516"><img class="se-7a5d3cc3" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/20/8f/209e319f00c52dddf231cafff593118f.jpg?wh=3500x2461"></div><div class="se-3268a253" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2517"><img class="se-f60c07cf" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/0b/11/0b1b5f81611626d8326a2dc05ce9aa11.jpg?wh=9184x4509"></div><div class="se-29a4d2a7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2518"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2519"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2519:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">四讲的顺序可以概括为四个字：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2520"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2520:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-27f01211" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">选 → 压 → 探 → 融。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-2ee312ec" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2521"><img class="se-957c3481" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/e6/8e/e6b05f9deaac2a02913b2164d068148e.jpg?wh=3202x2349"></div><div class="se-57ea810c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2522"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2523"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2523:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一讲，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2524"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2524:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-87025e82" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文分诊（Context Triage）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2525"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2525:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。解决的是哪些信息应该进入上下文。不是所有文件、日志、规则都该一股脑儿塞给模型，而是要按 P0/P1/P2/P3 分级，把最关键的信息放到最该出现的位置。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9231a02e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2526"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2527"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2527:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二讲，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2528"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2528:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-a0801100" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">语义压缩（Semantic Compaction）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2529"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2529:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。解决的是“进了上下文之后，怎么瘦身”。长任务跑到几十轮之后，对话历史、tool 结果、错误日志都会膨胀，必须压缩，但不能把关键证据压没。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4ebcc42d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2530"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2531"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2531:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三讲，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2532"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2532:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6aae59bd" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">渐进发现（Progressive Discovery）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2533"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2533:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。解决的是“我一开始不知道相关信息在哪里”。面对一个陌生代码仓库，Agent 不能把 2000 个文件全读一遍，而要像工程师一样，先广扫，再精读，再沿着调用链深入。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-eca1f041  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2534"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2535"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2535:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第四讲，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2536"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2536:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c5997808" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">多模态融合（Multi-Modal Fusion）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2537"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2537:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。解决的是“图片、表格、日志、PDF、SQL 这些异类信息怎么进入 Agent”。有些内容应该保留为图片，有些内容应该转成文本，有些内容应该先过滤再进入主 Context。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3657372d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2538"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2539"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2539:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">在 2025 到 2026 年间（这真是 Agent 设计沉淀成型的黄金一年），工业界围绕 Agent 如何“看见世界”，其实有很多争论，都可以放进我们的感知模式组里面来探讨。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-649324c0  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2540"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2541"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2541:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-3435fbee" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第一，RAG 还是 Agentic Search？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-27e3cf37  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2542"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2543"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2543:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">信息是应该提前建索引、接到任务后检索 top-K，还是让 Agent 像工程师一样，自己搜索、读文件、沿着线索深入？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-cd97638f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2544"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2545"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2545:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-f1087862" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第二，窗口越大越好吗？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-08e282b2  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2546"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2547"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2547:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文窗口越来越长，但长窗口不等于可以不筛选。问题不是“能不能塞进去”，而是“塞进去之后模型还能不能稳定用好”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-5284ec1e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2548"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2549"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2549:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-87f66987" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第三，多模态内容保留为图，还是转成文本？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-7474b3ee  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2550"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2551"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2551:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">图片、表格、PDF、截图、日志进入 Agent 之前，到底该保留原样，还是先转成结构化文本？这取决于核心信号在空间关系里，还是在文字内容里。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ee3ea2cf  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2552"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2553"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2553:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-78964baa" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第四，分诊靠人写，还是算法自动？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-82843170  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2554"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2555"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2555:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">哪些信息优先进入上下文，是靠人写规则、靠算法自动判断，还是靠 schema 和权限系统强约束？不同场景会有不同答案。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f1dfc5bc  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2556"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2557"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2557:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这四个问题你也许有答案，也许还没有答案。接下来的四讲，其实正是围绕它们展开：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ae027f23" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2558"><div class="se-2736f7c6 se-4bae6668" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2559"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2560"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2560:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-44b641a6" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文分诊</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2561"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2561:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，回答什么信息该进来、什么该挡在外面。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-db5f80f9 se-a9959945" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2562"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2563"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2563:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-0a01de6f" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">语义压缩</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2564"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2564:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，回答信息进来之后，怎么变短但不丢关键证据。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d0425924 se-045e4c8b" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2565"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2566"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2566:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-81806868" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">渐进发现</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2567"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2567:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，回答一开始不知道信息在哪时，Agent 该怎么逐步找。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-39ac2f78 se-96c3d5fa" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2568"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2569"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2569:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-e53560bc" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">多模态融合</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2570"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2570:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，回答图片、表格、PDF、SQL、日志这些异类信息该怎么进入上下文。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-b01f5a4c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2571"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2572"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2572:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">学完这四讲，你会发现所谓“Agent 感知世界”，不是简单地把资料喂给模型，而是在设计一套信息流秩序：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2573"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2573:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-669bb583" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">什么先看，什么后看，什么压缩，什么保留，什么按需再取。</span></span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-dbe5ac48" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2574"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2575"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2575:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Perception Trace：给 Agent 的眼睛装一块仪表盘</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-51b5a8bb  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2576"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2577"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2577:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">在进入四个具体的感知模式之前，我们还要知道一个贯穿整个模块的重要概念：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2578"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2578:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-f6595a23" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Perception Trace（感知追踪）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2579"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2579:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-0672595e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2580"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2581"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2581:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">因为很多团队调 Agent 时有一个共同习惯：结果错了，就改 Prompt；再错，就换模型。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2334f732  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2582"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2583"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2583:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">但现在我们知道，很多问题既不是 Prompt 的问题，也不是模型的问题，而是 Agent 根本没看到关键材料。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-7c95e7d6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2584"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2585"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2585:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果没有 Perception Trace，你很难发现这一点。因为最终回答里看不出来 Agent 当时看到了什么、没看到什么。你只能看到结果，却看不到信息是如何进入上下文的。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a4f12346  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2586"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2587"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2587:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Perception Trace 要记录的不是模型最后说了什么，而是模型在开始推理之前经历了什么：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-683c9c6a" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2588"><div class="se-bc789a56 se-139c16ba"><span></span></div><div class="se-17518b04 se-e0e0978e"><span></span></div><div class="se-66a6b01c"><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-4a4ed0e7 se-cce1b5c2" data-code-line-number="7"></div></div><div class="se-5b2b6cc6"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2589"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2590"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2590:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">读了哪些文件</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2591"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2592"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2592:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">检索到了哪些内容</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2593"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2594"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2594:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">选中了哪些片段</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2595"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2596"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2596:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">丢弃了哪些材料</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2597"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2598"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2598:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">压缩了哪些历史</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2599"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2600"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2600:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">调用了哪些发现动作</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2601"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2602"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2602:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">关键证据最终落在上下文什么位置</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 140px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-c794fa1a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2603"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2604"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2604:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果用户问：订单为什么不能退款？而最终答案错了。这时候普通日志只能看到：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2797dd64" data-code-language="javascript" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2605"><div class="se-2960c36f se-88f5780a"><span></span></div><div class="se-0aaa0c2c se-4a91921e"><span></span></div><div class="se-88fb35bb"><div class="se-dc2d6ad0 se-1e79e371" data-code-line-number="1"></div></div><div class="se-29918a58"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2606"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2607"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2607:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">answer = </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2608"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2608:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-string" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">"该订单已超过退款期限"</span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 20px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-8f0a0288  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2609"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2610"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2610:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">而 Perception Trace 能告诉你：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2412c474" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2611"><div class="se-98a84504 se-a92a7a4f"><span></span></div><div class="se-6e1bf81c se-dafaa586"><span></span></div><div class="se-955b1185"><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="8"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="9"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="10"></div><div class="se-8ce41925 se-7ab95439" data-code-line-number="11"></div></div><div class="se-e76d771b"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2612"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2613"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2613:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">检索命中：47 条</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2614"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2615"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2615:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">进入 context：6 条</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2616"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2617"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2617:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">被丢弃：41 条</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2618"></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2619"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2620"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2620:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">关键证据：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2621"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2622"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2622:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">refund_policy_v3.md</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2623"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2624"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2624:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">→ 被排序到第 38 位</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2625"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2626"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2626:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">→ 未进入 context</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2627"></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2628"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2629"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2629:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">实际进入：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2630"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2631"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2631:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">refund_policy_v1.md</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 220px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-876972d3  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2632"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2633"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2633:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">此时核心问题就会暴露的比较清晰。上下文分诊、语义压缩、渐进发现和多模态融合四个模式都在做不同的信息处理动作。但它们最终都会留下同一种痕迹，就是信息从哪里来、为什么进来、为什么被压缩、为什么被丢弃，以及为什么被重新取回。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-829d9018  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2634"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2635"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2635:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这些痕迹合在一起，就是 Perception Trace。后面几讲里，我们还会陆续介绍：budget_usage、dropped_count、compression_ratio、p3_hit_rate…… 等等不同的感知指标，这些指标本质上都是 Perception Trace 的不同切面。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b49e1d7f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2636"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2637"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2637:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Perception Trace 就是 Agent 的行车记录仪，虽然它不能让 Agent 更聪明，但它能让工程师知道 Agent 当时到底看见了什么。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-868dd5b6" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2638"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2639"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2639:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知工程不是新瓶装新酒</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-fb862cdf  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2640"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2641"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2641:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">很多工程师听到“感知工程”，会以为这是 LLM 时代才有的新东西。其实不是，它和我们熟悉的很多工程纪律是同源的。这里的底层问题是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2642"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2642:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-7600103b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">在资源有限的情况下，怎么把最有用的信息，放到离计算最近的位置</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2643"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2643:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-af83f733  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2644"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2645"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2645:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">数据库查询优化早就在做这件事。我们不会把一张上亿行的表全拉回应用层，再用代码慢慢过滤。工程师会用 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2646" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2647"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2647:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">WHERE</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2648"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2648:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2649" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2650"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2650:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">JOIN</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2651"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2651:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2652" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2653"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2653:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">LIMIT</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2654"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2654:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，尽量在数据库层就筛掉无关数据，只把真正需要的结果送到应用层。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a4f9a750  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2655"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2656"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2656:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文分诊也是同一个逻辑。Agent 不应该把整个代码仓库、全部文档、所有日志都塞进上下文窗口，而应该先判断：这次推理真正需要哪些信息？哪些必须马上给模型？哪些只是备用，先放在工具或文件系统后面。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d0f2f904  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2657"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2658"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2658:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">再看操作系统的虚拟内存。RAM 很贵，所以只放热数据；磁盘便宜，所以放冷数据。系统不会把所有文件都加载到内存里，而是根据访问频率和任务需要，把最可能用到的东西放到最近的位置。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c5eeb435  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2659"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2660"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2660:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 的上下文窗口也可以这样理解：P0/P1 优先级的信息相当于热数据，应该直接进入上下文；P2 优先级信息可以压缩后进入；P3 级别的信息就不需要一开始就占窗口，留在数据库、文件系统、搜索工具后面，等模型真的需要时再取。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a92f63db  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2661"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2662"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2662:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">CDN 缓存也是同一种工程思想。热门内容靠近用户，冷门内容留在源站。这样不是因为源站没用，而是因为每一种信息都有自己的访问成本。Agent 系统里也是一样：高频、稳定、关键的信息，应该离模型更近；低频、长尾、可能无关的信息，不应该一开始就占用 prompt。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1e147864  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2663"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2664"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2664:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">甚至编辑工作也在做类似的事。一个成熟的内容编辑，不会把所有采访录音、背景资料、参考文献都原封不动塞进文章里，不加筛选。他会判断哪些是主线，哪些是证据，哪些只是背景，哪些虽然有趣、但会干扰读者理解。感知工程在做的，也是在替模型完成这一步：先把信息整理成一个适合推理的现场。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6871b8f0  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2665"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2666"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2666:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以，感知工程不是一套完全陌生的新方法。它本质上是在 LLM 这个新载体上，重新实现数据库、操作系统、缓存系统早就积累过的经验。区别只在于，过去我们优化的是查询计划、内存页面、缓存命中率；现在我们优化的是上下文窗口、attention 预算和推理质量。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-28634a8c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2667"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2668"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2668:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-20e53bc8" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">离模型越近的信息越贵，所以不能谁都进来。感知工程，就是在决定谁有资格进入模型的工作记忆（也就是认知上下文）。</span></span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-84793e53" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2669"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2670"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2670:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">总结一下</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-8c81d5a9  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2671"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2672"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2672:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">上面所有内容其实都回到同一个问题：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2673"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2673:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-64dad854" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">你的 Agent 到底怎样感知世界？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-f1809092  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2674"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2675"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2675:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这个问题并不是 LLM 时代凭空冒出来的。Karpathy 曾有个类比：LLM 像 CPU，上下文窗口像 RAM，文件系统像磁盘。沿着这个类比看，感知就不是 prompt 前面的一点预处理，而是一条完整的信息流 pipeline。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-19824805  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2676"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2677"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2677:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">信息从哪里来，经过哪一层筛选，哪些进入上下文，哪些被压缩，哪些被丢弃，哪些留在工具和文件系统后面按需再取——这些决定合在一起，构成了 Agent 眼里的世界。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4098700f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2678"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2679"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2679:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知层的错误很容易一路传导到后面。如果某个版本之后，Agent 效果突然下降。团队一开始以为是模型变了，或者 prompt 改坏了，于是反复调 prompt、换模型、改系统指令。但最后 trace 拉出来才发现，真正的问题在更上游：数据源格式变了，原来的分诊规则没有跟上，导致每次都会漏掉一部分关键文件。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f34635c2  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2680"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2681"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2681:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这就是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2682"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2682:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-53d363e5" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">感知追踪（Perception Trace）</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2683"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2683:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">的意义。它通过对信息流的记录让我们知道 Harness 选了啥，Agent 读了啥，关键证据最后落在了上下文的什么位置。后面几讲中我们会介绍一系列的“</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2684"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2684:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-8e3b5c28" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">感知指标</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2685"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2685:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">”，把“感知决策”变成一个可观察、可度量、可调试的工程对象。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1b4e10e8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2686"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2687"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2687:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">对于 Agent 的感知，原则是：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2688"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2688:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c91760ee" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">少背 Prompt 术语，多看信息流。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-c65467fb  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2689"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2690"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2690:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Anthropic 在 2026 年的《</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2691" class="se-f828cddd se-8ab6c248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2692"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2692:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agentic Coding Trends Report</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2693"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2693:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">》里把上下文工程称为 AI 时代开发者最重要的技能转型之一。这个判断背后，其实就是同一个逻辑：未来开发者不只是写代码、写 prompt，还要设计 Agent 的信息流。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-cb5ee2a4  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2694"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2695"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2695:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">最后再强调一次：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2696"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2696:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c960de21" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">感知不是预处理，是核心架构问题。</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2697"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2697:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它和数据建模、API 设计、容量规划是一个量级的事情。你把它当配菜，Agent 就会在看似聪明的输出里不断漏信号；你把它当主菜，系统才有机会跑得稳、跑得准，也跑得便宜。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-5a7385ee" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2698"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2699"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2699:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">思考题</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-b271cbf8" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2700"><div class="se-77915ef4" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2701"><div class="se-6645b83b se-ffe6ded0" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-2cf48d70"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2702"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2702:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你当前 Agent 的系统提示词有多少 token？里面有多少内容是你觉得“为了让 Agent 知道更多”塞进去的？如果把这些为完整性服务的内容砍掉 50%，Agent 的关键任务表现会变好还是变差？为什么？</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-cc9725c1" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2703"><div class="se-5a30d0dd se-5aac3d45" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-d85c4484"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2704"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2704:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">找一个最近失败或者结果明显不稳定的 Agent 任务，复盘它到底看见了什么。这就是 Perception Trace。</span></span></span></div></div></div><div class="se-a6a1bf27  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2705"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2706"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2706:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">提示：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-fa1180cc" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2707"><div class="se-aacae908 se-4d27113f"><span></span></div><div class="se-84eb97ce se-d336a45b"><span></span></div><div class="se-eaae7e0f"><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-41c72f93 se-450ba372" data-code-line-number="8"></div></div><div class="se-0f439f05"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2708"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2709"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2709:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">任务是什么：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2710"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2711"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2711:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 最后错在哪里：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2712"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2713"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2713:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">正确答案依赖的关键证据是什么：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2714"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2715"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2715:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这个证据原本在哪里：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2716"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2717"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2717:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它有没有进入上下文：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2718"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2719"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2719:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果进了，出现在上下文什么位置：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2720"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2721"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2721:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果没进，是检索没命中、分诊丢掉了，还是压缩时压没了：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2722"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2723"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2723:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">下一版你会怎么改感知 pipeline：</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 160px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-2b3705e3" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2724"><div class="se-c79c31d4" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2725"><div class="se-9b363560 se-aca8a1ef" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-39b06903"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2726"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2726:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果有条件，为自己的项目做一个简单的实验设计：给 Agent 同一个任务、不同长度的 context（30K / 100K / 200K），看它的成功率会如何变化。</span></span></span></div></div></div><h2 class="se-e2da0167" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2727"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2728"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2728:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">下一讲预告</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-96ad403e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2729"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2730"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2730:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">感知是 Agent 跟世界打交道的入口闸。它决定 Agent 能看见什么，也就决定 Agent 能想什么。接下来的四讲，我们就围绕这道入口闸展开：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a7bfff96" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2731"><div class="se-2700dc85 se-dd9d32c6" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2732"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2733"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2733:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-671b0d11" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文分诊</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2734"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2734:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，讲什么信息应该进来，什么信息应该挡在外面。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-dbcabc09 se-9dae6394" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2735"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2736"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2736:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ce742e11" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">语义压缩</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2737"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2737:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，讲信息进来之后，怎么变短，但不丢关键证据。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1e89e3f5 se-2c096a24" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2738"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2739"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2739:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-02eb6e8b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">渐进发现</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2740"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2740:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，讲一开始不知道信息在哪里时，Agent 应该怎么找。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6612aa28 se-51a93c1b" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2741"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2742"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2742:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-99b50411" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">多模态融合</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2743"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2743:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，讲图片、表格、PDF、SQL、日志这些异类信息，应该怎么进入上下文。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-c9d3e9c8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2744"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2745"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2745:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">下一讲我们将真正进入的一个模式——“上下文分诊”的细节，这个模式会如何在工程上解决把“选什么进 context”这件事呢？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-db34ca7a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2746"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2747"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2747:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">我们下一讲见。</span></span></span></div></div>